{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you are so young, you know, a couple of years is an eternity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we decided that we are going to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the others decided that they are going to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had papers, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had papers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you didn't-- I don't-- I-- I don't think-- No, I don't-- maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I really don't remember that bit again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, I sort of-- I didn't retain that bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just know there were false paper, because I think they were under our-- they were under our name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think they were just falsified, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not really--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Milano, we-- we-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- I just know that we were told that we-- we went on a ship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was not really a ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It were literally-- Proteus, I think it was called, Proteus.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we literally-- it just came to me now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We literally slept one on-- we were really sort of, you know, like-- like sardines, but this way, not standing up, but this way, one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was just-- And it-- the-- the ship wasn't a ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was like an old vault or something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were already girls that were pregnant, you know As a matter of fact, I met my best friends, who, later on, became my best friends in Cyprus-- I'm going ahead-- I met on this ship.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Raisa and Mono Wurtzel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "W-U-R-Z-E-L, Raisa and Mono Wurtzel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
